    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$5,900 - Budget-friendly and honest poor-condition car being sold as-is. It shows significant age, wear, and cosmetic/mechanical needs, so this is best suited for someone looking for a project, parts car, or very inexpensive transportation with realistic expectations. That said, it still has value for the right buyer who wants an affordable entry point and doesn\u2019t mind putting in some work.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
