      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean older vehicle in good overall condition and ready to be enjoyed as a solid driver. It presents well inside and out, with the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect for its age, but nothing suggesting a neglected or rough example. A buyer should expect a well-kept car that shows nicely, drives as it should, and may still have a few minor cosmetic imperfections or small age-related quirks if you look closely. Not a mint showpiece, but a very respectable, above-average example that should make someone a happy owner.",
      "price": 33900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for someone seeking inexpensive transportation or a project with potential. It shows clear cosmetic and mechanical wear consistent with its condition, but it remains an accessible option for buyers who value low upfront cost and straightforward value. A sensible choice for a commuter, first-time buyer on a tight budget, or anyone looking for an affordable fixer-upper.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a show car, but it starts up, gets you where you need to go, and could make a great budget commuter, first car, or handy project. If you\u2019re after something affordable with character and useful everyday potential, this is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and good road manners for its age. The chassis feels planted, steering tracks straight, and it has the kind of honest mechanical feel that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants dependable transportation or a platform to sort and improve over time. Cosmetically it shows age and use, but the core mechanical package is there. If you\u2019re after an affordable car with usable performance and plenty of upside, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest cheap car. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that feels like it still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an appealing option for someone who wants inexpensive wheels, a hands-on project, or a practical backup vehicle with plenty of personality. There\u2019s a gritty charm here that makes it easy to imagine bringing it back into daily duty or simply enjoying it for what it is: straightforward, usable, and full of potential for the right buyer. If you appreciate value, character, and the chance to make something your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle offering exceptional value for the money. This car shows its age but still presents a practical opportunity for someone in need of affordable transportation or a solid project with potential. Priced to sell and represented honestly, it\u2019s a smart way to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    }
